PCLake	!tDBedDetS = tDMortVegS	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Derivatives		0

PCLake	vDeltaS = (tDIMS / cRhoIM + (tDHumS + tDDetS) / cRhoOM)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		0						
PCLake	! 'turnover depth' [m/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Derivatives		0						
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		0						
PCLake	! Assumption: volume change at top is corrected by an equal volume buried at 	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Derivatives		0						
PCLake	! the bottom.	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Derivatives		0						
PCLake	! in case of net settling: burial based on concentrations in top layer.	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Derivatives		0						
PCLake	! in case of net loss: burial based on concs. in 'deep' or unaffected sediment.	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Derivatives		0						
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		0						
PCLake	IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN	FALSE	IF	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives	1	1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tDBurIM = ( (tDHumS + tDDetS) + (cRhoOM / cRhoIM) * tDIMS ) /  &	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	             ( (sDHumS + sDDetS) / sDIMS + cRhoOM / cRhoIM )	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tDBurOM = (sDHumS + sDDetS) / sDIMS * tDBurIM	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tDBurDet = sDDetS / (sDHumS + sDDetS) * tDBurOM	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tDBurHum = tDBurOM - tDBurDet	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tDBurTot     = tDBurIM + tDBurOM	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tPBurHum     = rPDHumS * tDBurHum	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tPBurDet     = rPDDetS * tDBurDet	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tPBurAIM  = sPAIMS / sDIMS * tDBurIM	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tPBurPO4     = sPO4S * (vDeltaS / cDepthS)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	     ! burial flux of dissolved P [gP/m2/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tPBurTot     = tPBurDet + tPBurHum + tPBurAIM + tPBurPO4	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tNBurHum     = rNDHumS * tDBurHum	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tNBurDet     = rNDDetS * tDBurDet	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tNBurNH4     = sNH4S * (vDeltaS / cDepthS)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	     ! burial flux of dissolved NH4 [gN/m2/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tNBurNO3     = sNO3S * (vDeltaS / cDepthS)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	     ! burial flux of dissolved NO3 [gN/m2/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tNBurTot     = tNBurDet + tNBurHum + tNBurNH4 + tNBurNO3	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tSiBurDet    = rSiDDetS * tDBurDet	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tSiBurTot    = tSiBurDet	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		1		IF (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	ELSE	FALSE	ELSE	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tDBurIM = ( (tDHumS + tDDetS) + (cRhoOM / cRhoIM) * tDIMS ) /  &	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	             ( fDOrgSoil / (1.0 - fDOrgSoil) + cRhoOM / cRhoIM )	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tDBurOM = fDOrgSoil / (1.0 - fDOrgSoil) * tDBurIM	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tDBurDet = 0.0	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tDBurHum = tDBurOM	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tDBurTot = tDBurIM + tDBurOM	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tPBurHum = cPDSoilOM * tDBurHum	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tPBurDet = 0.0	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tPBurPO4 = cPO4Ground * (bPorS * vDeltaS)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tPBurAIM = 0.0  ! (simplification)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tPBurTot = tPBurHum + tPBurAIM + tPBurPO4	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tNBurHum = cNDSoilOM * tDBurHum	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tNBurDet = 0.0	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tNBurNO3 = cNO3Ground * (bPorS * vDeltaS)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tNBurNH4 = cNH4Ground * (bPorS * vDeltaS)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tNBurTot = tNBurHum + tNBurNH4 + tNBurNO3	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tSiBurDet = 0.0	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	   tSiBurTot = 0.0	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (vDeltaS .GE. 0.0) THEN				
PCLake	ENDIF	FALSE	ENDIF	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives	-1	0						
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		0						
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		0						
PCLake	!-----------------------------------------------------------------------	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Derivatives		0						
PCLake	! Water depth change due to sediment turnover:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Derivatives		0						
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Derivatives		0						
PCLake	IF (ConstDepth) THEN	FALSE	IF	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives	1	1		IF (ConstDepth) THEN				
PCLake	   vDeltaW = 0.0	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IF (ConstDepth) THEN				
PCLake	ELSE	FALSE	ELSE	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives		1		IFNOT (ConstDepth) THEN

PCLake	ENDIF	FALSE	ENDIF	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives	-1	0

PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Driver		0						
PCLake	! Other DYNAMIC code: (executed every OutInt)	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Driver		0	! Other DYNAMIC code: (executed every OutInt)					
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Driver		0						
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Driver		0						
PCLake	TERMT (Time .GE. EndTime)	FALSE	Control	Not in Excel	Driver		0	TERMT (Time .GE. EndTime)					
PCLake	! Go to TERMINAL if EndTime is reached	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Driver		0	! Go to TERMINAL if EndTime is reached					
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Driver		0						
PCLake	END  !of DYNAMIC	FALSE	Control	Not in Excel	Driver		0	END  !of DYNAMIC					
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Driver		0						
PCLake	!------------------------------------------------------------------	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Driver		0	!------------------------------------------------------------------					
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Driver		0						
PCLake	TERMINAL	FALSE	Control	Not in Excel	Driver		0	TERMINAL					
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Driver		0						
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Driver		0						
PCLake	END ! of TERMINAL	FALSE	Control	Not in Excel	Driver		0	END ! of TERMINAL					
PCLake	END ! of PROGRAM PCLake	FALSE	Control	Not in Excel	Driver		0	END ! of PROGRAM PCLake					
PCLake	!----------------------------------------------------------------------	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLake	"      FUNCTION SMPULSE(mVar, x, i, nm, tw)"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"C       Call: e.g. uVar = SMPULSE(mVar, Time, iPulse, nmVarMax, PulseWidth)"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"C       Smooth pulse, starting at the stated time and top at 0.5*tw later."	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"C       Uses the data in the TABLE array mVar: 1 to n = values, "	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C          n+1 to 2n = times.	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"C       nm = max. number of data values, tw = width of pulse."	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C       The count (i) should be initialized in the model.	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLake	$	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C     (Dollar sign means: model variables are accessible in this function.)	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"      INTEGER i, nm, Size"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"      DOUBLEPRECISION mVar(2*nm), x, tw"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLake	      IF(x .LT. mVar(nm+i)) THEN	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	         SMPULSE = 0.0	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	      ELSE IF(x .LE. mVar(nm+i)+tw) THEN	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	         SMPULSE = 1.0/tw * (COS(2*Pi*(x-mVar(nm+i)-0.5*tw)/tw) + 1.0)	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	     &   * mVar(i)	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	           ELSE	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	           SMPULSE = 0.0	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	           i = i + 1	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	      ENDIF	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLake	      RETURN	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	      END	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLake	C***********************************************************************	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"      DOUBLEPRECISION FUNCTION WindFunc(WindSpeed,FetchLength,"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"     &                                  WaterDepth,SedRoughness)"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"      DOUBLEPRECISION WindSpeed,FetchLength,WaterDepth,"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	     &                SedRoughness	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"        DOUBLEPRECISION Grav, Pi, RhoW, F_s, D_s, H_s, T_s"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"        DOUBLEPRECISION H, T, L_0, L, a_lm, U_bg, f_wg"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C       TauWind  : shear stress by wind action	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        Grav  =    9.8	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        Pi    =    3.141592	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        RhoW  = 1000.0	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C--------------------------------CHECK for WindSpeed > 0	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        IF ( WindSpeed .LT. 0.0001 ) THEN	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	          WindFunc = 0.0D0	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	          RETURN	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        ENDIF	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C--------------------------------TauWind calculation:	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        F_s = Grav*FetchLength/(WindSpeed**2)	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        D_s = Grav*WaterDepth/(WindSpeed**2)	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"C       WRITE(6,*)'F_s = ',F_s,' D_s = ', D_s"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        H_s = 0.24 * DTANH( 0.710 * D_s ** 0.763 ) * DTANH(	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	     &        ( 0.015 * F_s ** 0.45 ) / DTANH( 0.710 * D_s ** 0.763 ))	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        T_s = 2.0 * Pi * DTANH( 0.855 * D_s ** 0.365 ) * DTANH(	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	     &        ( 0.0345 * F_s ** 0.37 ) / DTANH( 0.855 * D_s ** 0.365 ))	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"C       WRITE(6,*)'H_s = ',H_s,' T_s = ', T_s"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        H = ( H_s * WindSpeed**2 ) / Grav	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        T = ( T_s * WindSpeed ) / Grav	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"C        WRITE(6,*)'H = ',H,' T = ', T"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        L_0 = ( Grav * T**2 ) / ( 2.0 * Pi )	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        L   = L_0 * DSQRT( DTANH( ( 2.0 * Pi * WaterDepth ) / L_0 ))	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"C       WRITE(6,*)'L_0 = ',L_0,' L = ', L"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        U_bg = ( Pi * H ) /	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	     &                  ( T * DSINH( (2.0 * Pi * WaterDepth) / L ) )	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        a_lm = ( U_bg * T ) / ( 2.0 * Pi )	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"C       WRITE(6,*)'U_bg = ',U_bg,' a_lm = ', a_lm"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        f_wg = 0.16 * DSQRT( SedRoughness / a_lm )	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	        WindFunc = f_wg * 0.5 * RhoW * U_bg**2	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	"C       WRITE(6,*)'f_wg = ',f_wg,' TauWind = ', TauWind"	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C--------------------------------RETURN	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	      RETURN	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	      END	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
PCLake	C----------------------------------------------------------------------	FALSE	Extra function	Not in Excel	Not in Excel		0						
		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0

PCLTran	 ! dilution of Blue [gP/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wNDilBlue = ukDil * sNBlueW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	 ! dilution of Blue [gN/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wDDilPhyt = wDDilDiat + wDDilGren + wDDilBlue	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	                             ! total algal dilution [gD/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wPDilPhyt = wPDilDiat + wPDilGren + wPDilBlue	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	                             ! total algal dilution [gP/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wNDilPhyt = wNDilDiat + wNDilGren + wNDilBlue	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	                             ! total algal dilution [gN/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   ! Total transport fluxes of algae:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wDTranDiat = uDLoadDiat / sDepthW - wDDilDiat 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wPTranDiat = uPLoadDiat / sDepthW - wPDilDiat 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wNTranDiat = uNLoadDiat / sDepthW - wNDilDiat 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wDTranGren = uDLoadGren / sDepthW - wDDilGren 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wPTranGren = uPLoadGren / sDepthW - wPDilGren 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wNTranGren = uNLoadGren / sDepthW - wNDilGren 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wDTranBlue = uDLoadBlue / sDepthW - wDDilBlue 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wPTranBlue = uPLoadBlue / sDepthW - wPDilBlue 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wNTranBlue = uNLoadBlue / sDepthW - wNDilBlue 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wDTranPhyt = wDTranDiat + wDTranGren + wDTranBlue	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	                             ! total algal transport flux [gD/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wPTranPhyt = wPTranDiat + wPTranGren + wPTranBlue	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	                             ! total algal transport flux [gP/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wNTranPhyt = wNTranDiat + wNTranGren + wNTranBlue	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	                             ! total algal transport flux [gN/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   ! Silica:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   uSiLoadSiO2  = cSiO2In * uQIn / mmPerm  ! SiO2 input [gSi/m2/d]	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   ! Note: is calculated from constant Si concentration in input water.	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   uSiLoadDet   = cSiDDetIn * uDLoadDet	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   uSiLoadDiat  = cSiDDiat * uDLoadDiat	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   uSiLoad = uSiLoadSiO2 + uSiLoadDet + uSiLoadDiat	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wSiDilSiO2 = ukDil * sSiO2W          ! [gSi/m3/d]	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wSiDilDet  = ukDil * sSiDetW ! [gSi/m3/d]	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wSiDilDiat = cSiDDiat * wDDilDiat     ! dilution [gSi/m3/d]	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wSiOutflTot = ukOut * (sSiO2W + sSiDetW + cSiDDiat * sDDiatW)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	            ! total surface outflow [gSi/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wSiTranSiO2 = uSiLoadSiO2 / sDepthW - wSiDilSiO2	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wSiTranDetW = uSiLoadDet / sDepthW - wSiDilDet	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   tSiTranTotT = uSiLoadSiO2 + uSiLoadDet + uSiLoadDiat  &	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	               - (wSiDilDet + wSiDilSiO2 + wSiDilDiat) * sDepthW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IF (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	ELSE	FALSE	ELSE	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   ! Dilution:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wPDilPhyt = ukDil * sPPhytW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	 ! dilution of Phyt [gP/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wNDilPhyt = ukDil * sNPhytW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	 ! dilution of Gren [gN/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wDDilPhyt = ukDil * sDPhytW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	  ! dilution of Blue [g/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   ! Total transport fluxes of algae:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wDTranPhyt = uDLoadPhyt / sDepthW - wDDilPhyt 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wPTranPhyt = uPLoadPhyt / sDepthW - wPDilPhyt 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wNTranPhyt = uNLoadPhyt / sDepthW - wNDilPhyt 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   ! Silica:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wSiTranSiO2 = 0.0	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   wSiTranDetW = 0.0	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	   tSiTranTotT = 0.0	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		1		IFNOT (InclThreeAlg) THEN				
PCLTran	ENDIF	FALSE	ENDIF	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	-1	0

PCLTran	!Zooplankton migration:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLTran	wDTranZoo   = ukDil * (cDZooIn - sDZoo) !migration flux [gD/m3/d]	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran	          !migration flux [gD/m3/d] (to prevent irreversible extinction)	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLTran	wPTranZoo   = ukDil * (cPDZooRef*cDZooIn - sPZoo)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0

PCLTran	             !Net migration flux [gN/m3/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0

PCLTran	wDTranDetW  = uDLoadDet / sDepthW - wDDilDet	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLTran	wO2TranW     = wO2Inflow - wO2Outfl	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLTran	wPTranPO4W  = uPLoadPO4 / sDepthW - wPDilPO4	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran	wPTranAIMW = uPLoadAIM / sDepthW - wPDilAIM	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran	wPTranDetW = uPLoadDet / sDepthW - wPDilDet	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLTran	wNTranNH4W = uNLoadNH4 / sDepthW - wNDilNH4	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran	wNTranNO3W = uNLoadNO3 / sDepthW - wNDilNO3	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran	wNTranDetW = uNLoadDet / sDepthW - wNDilDet	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0

PCLTran	! Total dilution fluxes [g/m3/d]:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLTran	wDDilTot = wDDilIM + wDDilDet + wDDilPhyt	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran	wPDilTot = wPDilDet + wPDilPO4 + wPDilAIM + wPDilPhyt	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran	wNDilTot = wNDilDet + wNDilNO3 + wNDilNH4 + wNDilPhyt	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran	wSiDilTot = wSiDilDet + wSiDilSiO2 + wSiDilDiat 	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0

PCLTran	! Mass balance equations [g/m2/d]:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLTran		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLTran	tDTranTotT = uDLoad - wDDilTot * sDepthW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran	tPTranTotT = uPLoad - wPDilTot * sDepthW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLTran	tNTranTotT = uNLoad - wNDilTot * sDepthW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0

PCLAbio		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLAbio	tNAbioNH4S  = tNInfNH4W - tNInfNH4S + (1.0-fRefrDetS) * tNMinDetS + tNMinHumS &	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLAbio	      - tNResusNH4 - tNDifNH4 - tNDifGroundNH4 - tNNitrS	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLAbio	tNAbioNO3S  = tNInfNO3W - tNInfNO3S + tNNitrS - tNDenitS  &	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLAbio	- tNResusNO3 - tNDifNO3 - tNDifGroundNO3	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0

PCLAbio	tNAbioHumS  = uNErosOM + fRefrDetS * tNMinDetS - tNMinHumS	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLAbio	                                !sediment humus [gD/m2/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLAbio		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0

PCLAbio	              - tNInfNO3S - tNDifGroundNO3 - tNDifGroundNH4	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0

PCLAbio		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0

PCLBed	!ENDIF	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	     ! mortality flux of vegetation (incl. logistic correction) [g.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	"     ! Mortality high if FlagLengHib&Spec = 1, otherwise low. "	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	    !Note: cannot be negative.	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0

PCLBed	! Assimilation and egestion by herbivorous birds:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	"! Note: assim. efficiency (fDAssBird) assumed equal for D,P and N."	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLBed	tDAssVegBird = fDAssBird * tDGrazVegBird	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	tDEgesBird   = tDGrazVegBird - tDAssVegBird	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLBed	tPAssVegBird  = fDAssBird * tPGrazVegBird	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	tPEgesBird    = tPGrazVegBird - tPAssVegBird	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	tPEgesBirdPO4 = fDissEgesBird * tPEgesBird	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	tPEgesBirdDet = tPEgesBird - tPEgesBirdPO4	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLBed	tNAssVegBird  = fDAssBird * tNGrazVegBird	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	tNEgesBird    = tNGrazVegBird - tNAssVegBird	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	tNEgesBirdNH4 = fDissEgesBird * tNEgesBird	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	tNEgesBirdDet = tNEgesBird - tNEgesBirdNH4	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLBed	!-----------------------------------------------------------------------	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	! FLUXES to/from Vegetation module to other components:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLBed	wDBedDetW = (tDMortVegW  + tDEgesBird) / sDepthW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total DW flux from Vegetation module to water detritus [gD.m-3.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	tDBedDetS = tDMortVegS	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total DW flux from Vegetation module to sediment detritus [gD.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	tDBedTotT = tDMigrVeg + tDProdVeg - tDRespVeg - tDManVeg - tDAssVegBird	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total DW flux from Vegetation module [gD.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLBed	wPBedPO4W = (- tPUptVegW + tPExcrVegW + tPMortVegPO4W + tPEgesBirdPO4) /sDepthW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total P flux from Vegetation module to PO4 in water [gP.m-3.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	wPBedDetW = (tPMortVegDetW + tPEgesBirdDet) / sDepthW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total P flux from Vegetation module to water detritus [gP.m-3.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	tPBedPO4S = - tPUptVegS + tPExcrVegS + tPMortVegPO4S	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total P flux from Vegetation module to pore water PO4 [gP.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	tPBedDetS = tPMortVegDetS	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total P flux from Vegetation module to sediment detritus [gP.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	tPBedTotT = tPMigrVeg - tPManVeg - tPAssVegBird	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total P flux from Vegetation module [gP.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLBed	wNBedNH4W = (- tNUptNH4VegW + tNExcrVegW + tNMortVegNH4W + tNEgesBirdNH4) &	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	/ sDepthW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total N flux from Vegetation module to NH4 in water [gN.m-3.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	wNBedNO3W =  - tNUptNO3VegW / sDepthW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total N flux from Vegetation module to NO3 in water [gN.m-3.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	wNBedDetW = (tNMortVegDetW + tNEgesBirdDet) / sDepthW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total N flux from Vegetation module to water detritus [gN.m-3.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	tNBedNH4S =  - tNUptNH4VegS + tNExcrVegS + tNMortVegNH4S	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total N flux from Vegetation module to NH4 in pore water [gN.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	tNBedNO3S =  - tNUptNO3VegS	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total N flux from Vegetation module to NO3 in pore water [gN.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	tNBedDetS =  tNMortVegDetS	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total N flux from Vegetation module to sediment detritus [gN.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	tNBedTotT = tNMigrVeg - tNManVeg - tNAssVegBird	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! total N flux from Vegetation module [gN.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLBed	! Total macrophytes OXYGEN fluxes:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLBed	tO2UptNO3VegW = O2PerNO3 * molO2molN * tNUptNO3VegW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! O2 production due to NO3 uptake from water by macrophytes [gO2.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	tO2UptNO3VegS = O2PerNO3 * molO2molN * tNUptNO3VegS	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	  ! O2 production due to NO3 uptake from sed. by macrophytes [gO2.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLBed	tO2BedW = tO2ProdVegW - tO2RespVegW + tO2UptNO3VegW	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	!total water O2 flux in vegetation module [gO2.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed	tO2BedS = tO2ProdVegS - tO2RespVegS + tO2UptNO3VegS	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLBed	!total sediment O2 flux in vegetation module [gO2.m-2.d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLBed		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0

PCLWeb	CONSTANT    cDBentIn    = 0.01   !external zoobenthos density [gD/m2]	FALSE	Parameter	Parameters(NOT Switch AND NOT Conversion)	Parameters(NOT Switch AND NOT Conversion)		0						
PCLWeb	CONSTANT    kMigrBent   = 1.0D-3  !zoobenthos migration rate [d-1]	FALSE	Parameter	Parameters(NOT Switch AND NOT Conversion)	Parameters(NOT Switch AND NOT Conversion)		0						
PCLWeb	                                  !Note: taken equal for all groups.	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0

PCLWeb	!PROCESSES OF HERBIVOROUS ZOOPLANKTON:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLWeb	uFunTmZoo = EXP( -0.5/cSigTmZoo**2 * ( (uTm-cTmOptZoo)**2 - &	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	           (cTmRef-cTmOptZoo)**2 ) )	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	                                   !temp. function of zooplankton [-]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLWeb	!Nutrient ratios:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	rPDZoo = sPZoo / (sDZoo+NearZero)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	                            !   P/D ratio herb.zooplankton [mgP/mgDW]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	rNDZoo = sNZoo/(sDZoo+NearZero)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	                            !   N/C ratio herb.zooplankton [mgN/mgDW]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLWeb		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLWeb	!Processes of herbivorous zooplankton in DW:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLWeb	    !Food:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	oDFoodZoo = cPrefDiat * sDDiatW + cPrefGren * sDGrenW  &	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	            + cPrefBlue * sDBlueW + cPrefDet * sDDetW              	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	            !food for zooplankton [mgD/l]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLWeb	    !Grazing:	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLWeb	aFilt = cFiltMax * uFunTmZoo * hFilt / (hFilt + oDOMW)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	                                     !filtering rate [ltr/mgDW/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	ukDAssTmZoo = fDAssZoo * cFiltMax * uFunTmZoo * hFilt	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	"           !max. assimilation rate of zooplankton, temp. corrected [d-1]"	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	aDSatZoo    = oDFoodZoo / (hFilt + oDOMW)	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	               !food saturation function of zooplankton [-]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	ukDRespTmZoo = kDRespZoo * uFunTmZoo	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	                            !respiration constant of zooplankton [d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	ukDIncrZoo = ukDAssTmZoo - ukDRespTmZoo - kMortZoo	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	               !intrinsic rate of increase of zooplankton [d-1]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb		FALSE	Blank	Blank	Blank		0						
PCLWeb	"wDEnvZoo    = MAX(0.0, ukDIncrZoo / cDCarrZoo * sDZoo**2)"	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	             !environmental correction of zooplankton [mg/l/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	             !Note: cannot be negative.	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	wDAssZoo    = aDSatZoo * ( ukDAssTmZoo * sDZoo - wDEnvZoo )	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	             !assimilation of zooplankton [mg/l/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	wDConsZoo   = wDAssZoo / fDAssZoo	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	             !consumption of zooplankton [mg/l/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	wDConsDetZoo   = cPrefDet*sDDetW / oDFoodZoo * wDConsZoo	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	             !detritus consumption by zooplankton [mg/l/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	wDConsDiatZoo   = cPrefDiat*sDDiatW / oDFoodZoo * wDConsZoo	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	             !diatoms consumption by zooplankton [mg/l/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0						
PCLWeb	wDConsGrenZoo   = cPrefGren*sDGrenW / oDFoodZoo * wDConsZoo	FALSE	AUXIL	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)	Derivatives(NOT Derivatives)		0						
PCLWeb	              !greens consumption by zooplankton [mg/l/d]	FALSE	Comment	Comment	Comment		0
